column5: None other then Elite Series Pro, Kevin Van Dam!!  This guys is pretty good eh?!
Kevin Van who??? The man can certainly get the job done.
Ya he pulled a big one out in the end!  How many KVD baitcasters can they make!!!
lol thanks, fixed it... see what happens when i try to type to fast... lol
lmao I'm sure that KVD is surfing internet message boards right now! Well maybe KVD but certainly not Kevin Van Dam...

i know, if i just won the biggest tourney in fishing, and had a $500,000 cheque handed to me... FIRST thing i would do is jump on OFC and say "thank you" haha  ok, maybe I would... but only cause u guys here are just so freakin cool! lol and i have no life, wife would spend the money, so really, what else would i have to do?
Simply incredible.  Hard to find a way to argue that he is anything but the best tournament bass fisherman ever.
